  "data_caveat": "Single source (theoddsapi), pre-kickoff only, ~12-day window. The back/lay spread uses market='h2h' (best back) vs market='h2h_lay' (best lay) on the SAME capture grid; this is the DISPLAYED top-of-book spread, NOT depth-aware. The lay side is sparse: only 7 distinct capture times spanning 2026-06-13..2026-06-17 across 69 matches (n=3020 matched pairs), so treat venue/time-to-kickoff spread differences as INDICATIVE. Mean spreads are inflated by longshots; medians are the robust figure. No queue depth, matched volume or market impact is observable in this dataset (see framework_not_measurable)."
